against the growing drug trade, emphasis is shifting to treatment and 
prevention. Experts caution, however, that approaches including group therapy, 
Just Say No programs and methadone treatment have shown little success. Alan 
Levenson /Onyx, A. Tannenbaum /Sygma, John Giordano /Picture Group; Photo, 
COLOR, 
</P>
