gives health to the bones." Proverbs 17:22 says, "A cheerful heart is good 
medicine. . . ." 
</P>
<P>
Assuredly, Lucille Ball brought joy to hearts, health to bones and the best 
medicine anyone would want -- down-to-earth comedy. 
</P>
