youngsters. ; Photo, Greg Morton applauds himself after completing an event. ; 
Photo, Jess Porter rounds a turn in marathon run, one of eight events each 
youth had to enter, regardless of physical impairments. RICK CORRALES / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
