</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
HARRIS, WILLIE ED; TRADE SHOWS; GUNS; ARMS SALES; SEMIAUTOMATIC WEAPONS; 
CRIMINALS; WEAPONS SMUGGLING; GANGS -- LOS ANGELES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA050789-0068 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 53734 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 7, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part 1; Page 1; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
