<HEADLINE>
<P>
CRITICS' CHOICE: REDISCOVERING AMERICA'S VALUES BY FRANCES MOORE LIPPE 
(BALLANTINE BOOKS: $22.50; 352 PP.) 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Walter Russell Mead 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Both liberals and conservatives will feel that Lappe has succeeded in 
presenting their views fairly and completely. Original, provocative, sometimes 
exasperating, but always striking." Walter Russell Mead 
</P>
