1 -- Mike Davis is in the second year of a two-year contract. He received a 
$987,500 salary in 1988 and is guaranteed a $400,000 loan. 
</P>
<P>
2 -- Kirk Gibson is in the second year of a two-year contract. He received a 
$1-million signing bonus and a $1.5-million salary in 1988. 
</P>
<P>
3 -- Aldredo Griffin received a $200,000 signing bonus with his new contract. 
</P>
<P>
