<CORRECTION>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
In the chart of Angel contracts in Sunday's editions, some incentive provisions 
of Wally Joyner's contract were omitted due to a computer problem. Joyner 
receives $25,000 awards at 140 and 155 games; $50,000 for All-Star election; 
$50,000 for league MVP; $25,000 if he wins a Gold Glove, and $25,000 if he wins 
a Silver Slugger Award. 
</P>
