<P>
ZOO TEAM OMISSION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Sheryl Kornman's article (April 30) on the new Children's Zoo was both accurate 
and informative. Throughout the article she developed the theme of a 
well-coordinated team consisting of the owner, architects and specialty 
contractors. Unfortunately one key member of the team was not mentioned, 
specifically the general contractor, Ray Wilson Co. 
</P>
<P>
We are very proud of the accomplishments of the group assembled by Greater Los 
Angeles Zoo Assn., and we are very proud of our contribution to the Adventure 
Island project. 
</P>
<P>
CHRISTOPHER J. DURKEE 
</P>
<P>
Pasadena 
</P>
<P>
 Durkee is vice president of marketing of the Ray Wilson Co. 
</P>
