MISSION VIEJO PAIR DECIDE ON COLLEGES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Rence Pina, a first baseman for the Mission Viejo High School softball team, 
has signed a letter of intent to attend Cal State Long Beach and teammate Amy 
Bond, a center fielder, has signed to attend UC Santa Barbara, Mission Viejo 
Coach Jeff Cunningham said. 
</P>
